@host = http://localhost:8090
@deviceId = 1

### List all devices
GET {{host}}/cam/devices

### Get RTSP URLs for a device
GET {{host}}/cam/devices/{{deviceId}}/rtsp

### Snapshot - normal camera
GET {{host}}/cam/devices/{{deviceId}}/snapshot?cam=normal

### Snapshot - thermal camera
GET {{host}}/cam/devices/{{deviceId}}/snapshot?cam=thermal

# NOTE: Streaming endpoints return multipart/x-mixed-replace (MJPEG).
# They do not work in .http files — open them directly in a browser or VLC instead:
#   http://localhost:8090/cam/devices/1/stream/normal
#   http://localhost:8090/cam/devices/1/stream/thermal


### PTZ - absolute position (azimuth 0-3600 tenths-of-degree, elevation -900..900, absolute_zoom 0-1000)
POST {{host}}/cam/devices/{{deviceId}}/pantilt
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "azimuth": -100,
    "elevation": 0
}

### PTZ - zoom
POST {{host}}/cam/devices/{{deviceId}}/zoom
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "zoom": 0
}

### PTZ - continuous pan/tilt
POST {{host}}/cam/devices/{{deviceId}}/pantilt/continuous
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "pan": 0,
    "tilt": 10
}

### PTZ - stop continuous pan/tilt
POST {{host}}/cam/devices/{{deviceId}}/pantilt/continuous
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "pan": 0,
    "tilt": 0
}

### PTZ - continuous zoom
POST {{host}}/cam/devices/{{deviceId}}/zoom/continuous
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "zoom": 20
}

### PTZ - stop continuous zoom
POST {{host}}/cam/devices/{{deviceId}}/zoom/continuous
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "zoom": 0
}